author: The Film Theorists
description:
Ever noticed how Disney Animated movies seem to always have something to do with a star of some kind? Whether it be a wishing star, a star-shaped friend, or even the sun (yes, the sun is a star too!), it all seems to be a connecting point for Disney movies!
